<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Canon</title>
  <meta name="csrf-token" content="{{ csrfToken }}">
  {{ css('css/promotion') }}
</head>
<body>
  <div class="promotion-header container">
    <div class="columns">
      <div class="promotion-header-logo column">
        Easy Link Keeper
      </div>
      <div class="promotion-header-links column">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#promotion-features">Features</a></li>
          <li><a href="#promotion-team">Our team</a></li>
          <li><a href="#promotion-contact">Contact</a></li>
          <li><a href="/login" class="button is-primary">Go to login</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="promotion-call-to-action">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <h1 class="title">Manage proposals,<br> with better relations.</h1>
          <h2 class="subtitle">Easy Link Keeper allows you to keep all your information related to business contacts in one place, so you can manage them with ease!</h1>
          <a href="#promotion-features" class="button is-primary">See the features</a>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <img src="images/screenshot.png">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="promotion-features" class="promotion-features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns is-multiline">
        <div class="promotion-feature column is-one-third">
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="promotion-features-icon column is-3">
              <img src="images/proposal.svg">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <h3>Manage Proposals</h3>
              <p>Create and establish new relationships with companies, maintain them and gather information to ensure to reap the rewards in the profit!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="promotion-feature column is-one-third">
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="promotion-features-icon column is-3">
              <img src="images/insight.svg">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <h3>Gain insight</h3>
              <p>Be guided throughout the task of gaining information, our scoring will help you gain vital information and show you the progress you’ve made thus far.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="promotion-feature column is-one-third">
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="promotion-features-icon column is-3">
              <img src="images/act.svg">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <h3>Act on your best chances</h3>
              <p>Stop losing your cool and lose chances. With our tool you’re able to act on the chances that might be lingering right under your nose!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="promotion-feature column is-one-third">
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="promotion-features-icon column is-3">
              <img src="images/proposal.svg">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <h3>Manage proposals</h3>
              <p>Once you’ve established a relationship it’s time to work on the proposals. Ensure your position as a vital partner with our proposal management tool!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="promotion-feature column is-one-third">
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="promotion-features-icon column is-3">
              <img src="images/proposal.svg">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <h3>Get an overview</h3>
              <p>All the information you’d ever need, right at your fingertips. Stop using notes, documents and other timewasters and start using ELK!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="promotion-feature column is-one-third">
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="promotion-features-icon column is-3">
              <img src="images/proposal.svg">
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <h3>Vital information</h3>
              <p>ELK is sure to remind you about vital information, the devil is in the details and so are you after using our application!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="promotion-team" class="promotion-team">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="promotion-team-header column"><h2>Meet our team</h2></div>
      </div>

      <div class="promotion-team-members columns">
        <div class="promotion-team-member column">
          <div class="promotion-team-member-photo" style="background-image: url('images/vince.png')"></div>
          <h4>Vince van Noort</h4>
          <div>Software engineer</div>
        </div>
        <div class="promotion-team-member column">
          <div class="promotion-team-member-photo" style="background-image: url('images/jort.png')"></div>
          <h4>Jort van Gorkum</h4>
          <div>Software engineer</div>
        </div>
        <div class="promotion-team-member column">
          <div class="promotion-team-member-photo" style="background-image: url('images/niek.png')"></div>
          <h4>Niek Geijtenbeek</h4>
          <div>Mastermind of Algorithms</div>
        </div>
        <div class="promotion-team-member column">
          <div class="promotion-team-member-photo" style="background-image: url('images/tijmen.png')"></div>
          <h4>Tijmen van der Spijk</h4>
          <div>Communication and Sales</div>
        </div>
        <div class="promotion-team-member column">
          <div class="promotion-team-member-photo" style="background-image: url('images/madio.png')"></div>
          <h4>Madio seck</h4>
          <div>Communication and Sales</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="promotion-contact" class="promotion-contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="promotion-contact-header column"><h2>Get in touch</h2></div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns is-centered">
        <div class="promotion-contact-text column is-6">
          <p>If you have any questions, feel free to mail us at <a href="mailto:contact@easylinkkeeper.nl">contact@easylinkkeeper.nl</a>. <br>We will try to get to you as fast as possible!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
